{"tid":1067160,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲露營Camping、Caravan：你問我答 附4K車CAM片","createTime":"2019-03-18T10:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T13:27:23.000Z","uid":198021,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"718f030001fa0aae703a5dabb0cde2d371f51084","tid":1067160,"uid":198021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:42:46.000Z","msg":"響澳洲玩CAMPING值得一試（會上癮），玩法有好多種，<br />\n收錢、免費都試過<br />\n訓TENT、訓車；有電、冇電；有水、冇水都玩過<br />\nQueensland，New South Wales, Victoria 都留低過腳毛，<br />\n<br />\n一個字：好正<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩想知？你問我答（盡力）<br />\n<br />\n露營車營地Camp Site喺咩樣？去片：<br />\n4K露營車營地 - 車CAMP片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4WpsieYTGOg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4WpsieYTGOg&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=f1c6af4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4WpsieYTGOg</a><br />\n<br />\n免費Camp Site Camping片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Eug5IYOsRbM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEug5IYOsRbM&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=b2f481a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Eug5IYOsRbM</a><br />\n<br />\n（影片黎自YouTube）"},{"pid":"6bba1083324b6c301ab7280b0ff4ba975b060494","tid":1067160,"uid":134546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"蜘蛛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7254e3b1cb3040a8915c7544a8e236dbbad09b","tid":1067160,"uid":198021,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"6bba1083324b6c301ab7280b0ff4ba975b060494","tid":1067160,"uid":134546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"蜘蛛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:30:45.000Z","msg":"樹林、陰暗地方可能有。露營噶草坪未見到過蜘蛛~ 好彩"},{"pid":"7b76fdc69cf71795d347233fa703fad2988756f7","tid":1067160,"uid":113891,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"repl