.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4WpsieYTGOg&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=f1c6af4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4WpsieYTGOg</a><br />\n<br />\n免費Camp Site Camping片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Eug5IYOsRbM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEug5IYOsRbM&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=b2f481a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Eug5IYOsRbM</a><br />\n<br />\n（影片黎自YouTube）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:35:05.000Z","msg":"我去過cockatoo island"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"呢個鸚鵡島值得一提<br />\n如果想淺嘗下CAMPING訓室外の感覺、又唔想買GEAR，又唔想揸咁遠水路：<br />\nCockatoo island 響SYDNEY市區，提供曬帳篷訓覺等GEAR，入去住就得<br />\n<br />\n呢種玩法有個specific word：叫GLAMPING<br />\n<br />\n不過我未試過，巴打可唔可以分享下GLAMPING覺得點？"},{"pid":"0916245c50ec61793ba0a315d87eedaf7b42a501","tid":1067160,"uid":115584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"租車連埋油費大概幾多洗費？"},{"pid":"7ad669c55612298f763a654f63a64c5e895f56e2","tid":1067160,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:51:34.000Z","msg":"露營車可以係咩網有得租？<br />\n平均幾錢日租？打滿番個缸要幾錢？<br />\n揸起上黎難唔難操控？睇位如何？<br />\n同埋係咪一定要泊係指定地方？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8bb1f1f03e73d7cae650e0d4fac5a5f1ef335d","tid":1067160,"uid":198021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0916245c50ec61793ba0a315d87eedaf7b42a501","tid":1067160,"uid":115584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"租車連埋油費大概幾多洗費？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T20:33:27.000Z","msg":"租車同油費分開計，<br />\n<br />\nCAMPER VAN大約100蚊AUD一日，CAMPER VAN喺已經有動力、喺貨van改裝，唔需要另外租車，不過空間就比較tight，亦唔會似CARAVAN咁有廁所有廚房<br />\n<br />\nCARAVAN就喺拖住行果隻，從80-150不等，要再另租大馬力車去拖（SUV或UTE居多）。最主要喺部車要加裝了towbar，唔喺咁好租<br />\n<br />\n油費最平預1.5HKD/km（CAMPER VAN）、2-2.5HKD/km（拖caravan）"},{"pid":"b5d8b417127afa02a40a9d0f3375030b7e4859e3","tid":1067160,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T20:37:27.000Z","msg":"sydney附近有咩靚景既campground介紹，兩三個鐘車程冇問題， 去過Frazer幾正"},{"pid":"c6f1e39dd7dfea49bb4e5bcc1dce1b4ec20a3893","tid":1067160,"uid":198021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ad669c55612298f763a654f63a64c5e895f56e2","tid":1067160,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:51:34.000Z","msg":"露營車可以係咩網有得租？<br />\n平均幾錢日租？打滿番個缸要幾錢？<br />\n揸起上黎難唔難操控？睇位如何？<br />\n同埋係咪一定要泊係指定地方？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T20:39:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.apollocamper.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apollocamper.com%2F&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=c7a61d77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.apollocamper.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jucy.com.au/rental-locations/australia/sydney-airport/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jucy.com.au%2Frental-locations%2Faustralia%2Fsydney-airport%2F&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=8e1347fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jucy.com.au/rental-locations/australia/sydney-airport/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hippiecamper.com/campervan-hire-locations-sydney.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hippiecamper.com%2Fcampervan-hire-locations-sydney.aspx&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=05970fbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hippiecamper.com/campervan-hire-locations-sydney.aspx</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.britz.com/au/en/campervan-hire\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britz.com%2Fau%2Fen%2Fcampervan-hire&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=7f6db3b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.britz.com/au/en/campervan-hire</a><br />\n<br />\n比較出名幾間&uarr;<br />\n<br />\nCAMPERVAN好容易揸，停得普通車都可以停<br />\n<br />\nCARAVAN辛苦好多，特別喺往後入位，好難睇，通常要入CARAVAN PARK過夜，就好似頂post條片咁"},{"pid":"61bb728e91fc5b19c19e0e4066b66dedf63e9187","tid":1067160,"uid":198021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b5d8b417127afa02a40a9d0f3375030b7e4859e3","tid":1067160,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T20:37:27.000Z","msg":"sydney附近有咩靚景既campground介紹，兩三個鐘車程冇問題， 去過Frazer幾正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T20:54:06.000Z","msg":"推薦你三個APP/網<br />\n<br />\n1、CAMPERMATE：免費APP，可以搵campground，restarea<br />\n2、Google Map：用CAMPERMATE搵到後去Google Map睇睇評價review，外國人好鐘意用google map review，如果喺好噶campground一定多rating<br />\n3、專業級 - Camps Australia：每年都update的全澳洲camping、4WD聖經，資料最詳盡和準確，要幾十蚊AUD本。好彩出咗個APP，幾蚊雞就得。<br />\n<br />\nSydney有三個方向可以搵：<br />\n西：南山 - Katoomba為中心，設施最好，唔貴。附近一帶比較primative（平/免費），要重裝D。<br />\n南：Jervis Bay - Camp park多如牛毛，但一到holiday大幅升價、又難book。宜家入冬就冇咩人同你爭。<br />\n北：Lake Macquarie - 好靚、寧靜舒服，如果西南北比我揀我最鐘意北邊，再北D喺Forester/Myall Lake湖區，都喺我覺得最啱我的地方。因為我唔識衝浪，如果識可能會鐘意海灘多D。<br />\n<br />\nwithin 3hr都有好多其他選擇，不過太近市區我覺得冇feel"},{"pid":"28c3d56019d3c55a258251107f80e25ac2484528","tid":1067160,"uid":207426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T01:26:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e6b6da0cc5fde5727b26c61a0f99844519b36f9","tid":1067160,"uid":207426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T01:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"567e751719456193d58010d